01:08:59,801 --> 01:09:04,801
Jack!

847
01:09:09,686 --> 01:09:11,436
Oh, Jack.

848
01:09:11,437 --> 01:09:15,107
Thank God you're here.

849
01:09:15,108 --> 01:09:16,566
Jack.

850
01:09:16,567 --> 01:09:18,986
